Yeah.

393
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:15,829
- That's a good week's work, Vincenzo.
- Papa! Papa!

394
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:23,232
Papa, Papa, good news!
I sold the other daisy to Signor Biggio.

395
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:27,035
Ah, Tiny Anthony.
Come. Come.

396
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:29,469
Ah, you are such a good boy.
You know that?

397
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:32,956
