424
00:43:15,080 --> 00:43:17,799
Don't argue with your father.
God'll pluck your eyes out.

425
00:43:17,920 --> 00:43:20,195
It's a puppy.

426
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:27,355
- Must have cost you a fortune.
- Yes. But look how happy the boy is.

427
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:41,870
Someday, will I be able to run and play
like all the other children?

428
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:44,833
Yes, my son. Yes.

429
00:43:44,960 --> 00:43:47,793
And I promise you,
there will come a day...

430
00:43:47,920 --> 00:43:51,071
where your legs will be as strong
as any ox...

431
00:43:51,200 --> 00:43:54,397
and this--
this battered old crutch...

432
00:43:54,520 --> 00:43:56,795
